snippet.title: The Legend of Zelda: Dawn and Dusk [1080p Widescreen] - Part 1 [SPOILERS]
snippet.description:
Part one of my full playthrough of Dawn and Dusk mod for the Legend of Zelda: Ocarina of Time. If full resolution options aren't available, give YouTube time to process them.

Mod Credits:
Lead Development & Music
- Captain Seedy-Eye

64DD Porting
- LuigiBlood

Special Thanks to
- PK-LOVE
- BWXIX
- Hylian Modding (http://hylianmodding.com/)

Testers
- Captain Seedy-Eye
- LuigiBlood
- Hard4Games
- ZFG
- Dry4Haz
- Fig

Mod (Download can be found under "Releases"): https://github.com/LuigiBlood/zelda_dawn_dusk
